{
  "stem": "7506.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then things started, for me, to change a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for my family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was away from my neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was away from my friend Jopi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was away from everything that had become, shall I say, my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Down the street where we lived, there was a swimming pool which I used to go to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was open land where we used to play football.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I was taken-- we were taken-- to the eastern part of Amsterdam, which is known as the-- in Dutch, it's called-- called [DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It is-- it is this part of Amsterdam where all the streets and everything are named after South Africa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the names of the streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were moved to a place, a street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the address is-- was 60 [DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The [DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[DUTCH] is the name of a man-- a Dutch settler of the 1600s who went to South Africa.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "South Africa was Dutch originally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So all the streets are-- are Dutch names, but refer to places in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we lived in that street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in that street and in that building, that house-- it was a house with apartments, and we lived on the third floor of that apartment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I personally knew nobody there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a completely other area of Amsterdam, which I-- I don't think I'd ever been to before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there were non-Jewish people living there in that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know-- I can't remember how long it was that we moved from south Amsterdam to the east of Amsterdam to the Jewish quarter.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I don't remember how long I lived in that Jewish quarter until we also were deported from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember him going to visit me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
